body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Wilson Motors. My name is Gabriel Wilson. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, Gabriel. My name is Joan Jenkins.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Joan. In order to assist you better, may I please have your date of birth for verification?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's zero five slash one two slash one nine eight zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Joan. Can you also provide the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's nine eight seven six.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for the information, Joan. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today regarding our car dealership?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling excited about purchasing a new car and wanted to know more about the available financing options.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: That's great to hear, Joan! We have various financing options and I can help you explore those. Thank you for your time and interest in Wilson Motors. Have a wonderful day!
